Author: Ad_Mine
Title: [ANN] [pre-ICO] ðŸŒŽ ADMINE ðŸŒŽ - Monetizes all your activity on the Internet ðŸŒŽ
Body: Sorry, but I have to disagree with you, in fact there are only two real projects on the market that we can consider competitors, it's BitClave and Brave.  But the difference from them, our system is designed in such a way that users do not need to change the behavior of the network, using their usual search engines or applications.  Our system works with any browser, with any search engine, any application or game. Every owner of his website or application can connect to us for free.   to: happyme1818  Have you ever met similar projects? Can you share the name?   For advertising exchanges, an API has been created that will allow them to sell all unsold traffic for free and from the usual banners to make the most targeted CPA advertising.  Each publisher (owner of their own site or application or game) receives payment not for 1000 impressions or clicks, but for the user who is interested in the product.  Users can subscribe to favorite brands and view only the ads they themselves have chosen.  In our system, targeting is designed, analogues in the world which does not exist, advertisers search through smart contracts based on data within user questionnaires, each user decides what information he is willing to open for searching on his personal data and receives a reward in the form of coins for providing personal data for exact targeting.  We do not sell user data, smart contracts search within user profiles, leaving users anonymous on the network. The system shows only anonymous statistics on the fulfillment of the terms of the smart contracts. Each user can see a condition that has become decisive for his choice.  Our system has unique capabilities, such as: - evaluation of the quality of goods (interview among subscribers) - Testing games (you do not need to keep staff, you can attract a few thousand testers overnight in the world) - paid filters (any brand can create a unique targeting, add any new parameter which is not present in the questionnaires)  Users receive coins directly from advertisers for doing marketing quests and viewing ads. The advertiser himself determines what price he pays users for each viewing.  There are no intermediaries in the system, each participant of the system receives money directly, our system also does not take money for advertising campaigns, we take the commission only from operations on the wallet, to input and output of money.  Inside our wallet, it is possible to enter and withdraw money through a bank account, credit card, exchange through other payment systems or in the form of another crypto currency.

Author: Ad_Mine
Title: [ANN] [pre-ICO] ðŸŒŽ ADMINE ðŸŒŽ - Monetizes all your activity on the Internet ðŸŒŽ
Body: Our system is built on smart contracts.  Smart contracts are software aggregators, the tasks of which are: the choice of users to display advertising on personal data, monitor the implementation of the terms of the transaction and make payments.  Users remain anonymous in the system, providing their personal data only to smart contracts, no one else has access to the questionnaires.  The system is free of managers and brokers, all actions are performed automatically and are regulated only by smart contracts.  Personification of the system (we know exactly each user) removes the possibility of cheating bots or clickers. The architecture of the platform provides only static content, which removes the possibility of embedding malicious code.  A smart contract forms payment only upon the fulfillment of the conditions, it is independent and objective, any participant can see the performance statistics of its teams.  Each user can see based on what information he was found.

Author: Ad_Mine
Title: [ANN] [pre-ICO] ðŸŒŽ ADMINE ðŸŒŽ - Monetizes all your activity on the Internet ðŸŒŽ
Body: The price is always set by the advertiser.  AdMine makes targeted advertising.  Our main task is to determine the desire of the user. The fact is that today only 3 banners out of 10 show actual advertisement for the user.  Here is an example: there are 3 people who own BMW, Mercedes, Audi cars, respectively.  Our task is to show each of them a banner of the corresponding brand of the car.    in Whitepaper you write, that you have analyzed the markets of North and South America. Does it mean that these markets are a priority for you?  Of course, our system is aimed at the whole world, all devices.

Author: Ad_Mine
Title: [ANN] [pre-ICO] ðŸŒŽ ADMINE ðŸŒŽ - Monetizes all your activity on the Internet ðŸŒŽ
Body: Our tokens are not securities or an investment contract.  We sell custom tokens that will be used to purchase advertisements, just as any user can exchange Media Coins for any other crypto currency.  In order to determine, if token is a security token, we turn to the Howey test. A token of the Security Exchange Act of 1934, regulated by the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC). According to the Howey test, a token can be considered a security token if it satisfies all of the following conditions: The token is purchased as an investment contract; The investment is directed towards a common enterprise; The investor expects to gain passive profits at the expense of third parties;

The main point, investors do not need to look for someone to sell the token, users of our system will automatically redeem tokens from investors.  Additional information you can find on our website in the section of the token.  http://admine.io/

Author: Ad_Mine
Title: [ANN] [pre-ICO] ðŸŒŽ ADMINE ðŸŒŽ - Monetizes all your activity on the Internet ðŸŒŽ
Body: We would like to share some key information about our project:  Our system works with any browser, with any search engine, any application or game. Every owner of his website or application can connect to us for free.  For advertising exchanges, an API has been created that will allow them to sell all unsold traffic for free and from the usual banners to make the most targeted CPA advertising.  Each publisher (owner of their own site or application or game) receives payment not for 1000 impressions or clicks, but for the user who is interested in the product.  Users can subscribe to favorite brands and view only the ads they themselves have chosen.  In our system, targeting is designed, analogues in the world which does not exist, advertisers search through smart contracts based on data within user questionnaires, each user decides what information he is ready to open for search on his personal data and receives a reward in the form of coins for providing personal data for exact targeting.  We do not sell user data, smart contracts search within user profiles, leaving users anonymous on the network. The system shows only anonymous statistics on the fulfillment of the terms of the smart contracts. Each user can see a condition that has become decisive for his choice.  Our system has unique capabilities, such as: product quality evaluation (survey among subscribers), game testing (you do not need to keep staff, you can attract thousands of testers overnight in the world), paid filters (any brand can create unique targeting, add any new parameter of which is not present in the questionnaires)  Users receive coins directly from advertisers for doing marketing quests and viewing ads. The advertiser himself determines what price he pays users for each viewing.  There are no intermediaries in the system, each participant of the system receives money directly, our system also does not take money for advertising campaigns, we take the commission only from operations on the wallet, to input and output of money.  Inside our wallet, there is an opportunity to enter and withdraw money through a bank account, credit card, exchange through other payment systems or in the form of another crypto currency.  For more detailed information, please visit our website and read the Whitepaper. Also please take a look to our video presentation.

Author: Ad_Mine
Title: [ANN] [pre-ICO] ðŸŒŽ ADMINE ðŸŒŽ - Monetizes all your activity on the Internet ðŸŒŽ
Body: Admine erases the boundaries!  Have you ever thought that for all the advertising you see every day, you can get money for it?  Your personal mobile phone, computer tablet can work for you and bring you a whopping income, every day!  AdMine monetizes all your activity on the Internet without changing your usual search engines or applications.  Our system works with any browser, with any search engine, any application or game. Every owner of his website or application can connect to us for free.  All you need to do is: 1. You can log in through your account on social networks or register as a new user. 2. Fill in your profile and subscribe to any brands  This is all that is required of you!  From now on, every time you see a banner connected to our system, you get the Media Coin crypto currency.  You can withdraw Media Coin to your bank account or credit card, you can buy goods on the Internet or exchange for another crypto currency.  Imagine a world where you wake up in the morning, read news or view your favorite social networks and for every advertising banner you get a crypto currency!  AdMine system is multifaceted, you can expand your income with us, carry out marketing quests, test games, evaluate the quality of the goods of your favorite brands and get paid for all this!
